title: 'Shazam!' Rumor Reportedly Confirms Major Villains
excerpt: It sounds like the Seven Deadly Sins really will appear in Shazam!According to a report from [...]
description:
Makes sense, the movie does appear to be a loose adaptation of the Geoff Johns reboot (including the extended Marvel Family *ahem*).

I can see the movie probably using the alternate Seven Sins which frequent the Shazam/Captain Marvel books, which often exclude Lust ‘cause the protagonists are children.

…Not that this hasn’t stopped some creators writing stories with Captain Marvel/Shazam in (but not as the protagonist) where Lust is brought back for the more traditional seven deadly sins.

An example of this includes a villain in the Outsiders absorbing the sins to give himself a power-boost and using Lust to compel his henchmen into spontaneously having sex with each other (this isn’t protrayed as creepy as it should be). Or in a JLA/JSA crossover where the Sins possess various members from both of the teams, with Power Girl becoming the fleshsuit of Lust, where Lust compels to people to fight each other in the street in order to impress her.

But yeah, the traditional Shazam Sins please.
